Currently each comment takes up a substantial amount of vertical height given it is just a comment. There is a lot of white space above and below the comment and then when you combine the comment information, links and border box each comment takes up a lot of space. 

It would be great if each comment was much shorter in vertical height and far more streamlined - especially for threaded comments.

