When you view a historical version of a page, you see the old versioned page with a bunch of menu options on the tools menu. 

Most of the options on the tools menu will operate on and show information about the current page rather than the old version of that page. This is confusing and not intuitive.

For example, ideally the page info link would take you to the page info of the historical, versioned page.

